1037
01:22:44,614 --> 01:22:46,616
Daddy?

1038
01:22:46,741 --> 01:22:48,368
Daddy! I'm here, Daddy!

1039
01:22:48,535 --> 01:22:49,995
I'm here!

1040
01:23:07,640 --> 01:23:09,809
My husband's there now, watching them.

1041
01:23:09,935 --> 01:23:13,147
He sent me to call you so you could
do something before they get away.

1042
01:23:13,272 --> 01:23:15,149
It isn't as easy as all that.

1043
01:23:15,274 --> 01:23:19,404
My husband is in that chapel
waiting for me to bring help.

1044
01:23:20,405 --> 01:23:24,660
May I speak to Mr Buchanan?
He told me to call him if I needed him.

1045
01:23:24,785 --> 01:23:27,747
I'm awfully sorry.
I can't get in touch with him.

1046
01:23:27,914 --> 01:23:30,875
He's at an important diplomatic affair
at the Albert Hall.

1047
01:23:31,001 --> 01:23:33,211
